Employee - Class in io.github.imunsmart.employee
Employee class that contains name, username, password and email and sets up employee emails and passwords.
Employee(String, String) - Constructor for class io.github.imunsmart.employee.Employee
Initializes an employee object with a name and password, username is determined by name, if an invalid name is supplied, username is defaulted to 'default' and email is defaulted to 'user@oracleacademy.Test', if password is invalid it is defaulted to 'pw'.
Employee(String, String, String, String) - Constructor for class io.github.imunsmart.employee.Employee
Initializes an employee object with all fields, used when loading an employee record from the database.
employeeLogin(ActionEvent) - Method in class io.github.imunsmart.Controller
Gets information from text fields and attempts to login, fires when login button is pressed.
